menu "DHT20 Sensor (dsp_dht20)"

    config DSP_DHT20_SDA_PIN
        int "DHT20 I2C SDA GPIO number"
        default 8
        range 0 48
        help
            GPIO number for the I2C SDA line of the DHT20 sensor.
            Requires an external 4.7 kΩ pull-up resistor to 3.3 V.
            Default GPIO 8 is available on most ESP32-S3 development boards.

    config DSP_DHT20_SCL_PIN
        int "DHT20 I2C SCL GPIO number"
        default 9
        range 0 48
        help
            GPIO number for the I2C SCL line of the DHT20 sensor.
            Requires an external 4.7 kΩ pull-up resistor to 3.3 V.
            Default GPIO 9 is available on most ESP32-S3 development boards.

    config DSP_DHT20_I2C_PORT
        int "I2C peripheral port number (0 or 1)"
        default 0
        range 0 1
        help
            ESP32-S3 I2C peripheral index.  Use 0 unless port 0 is already
            occupied by another component.

endmenu
